---
import Logo from './ui/logo.astro';
---
<footer class="bg-gradient-to-r from-primary to-accent text-white">
  <div class="container mx-auto py-12 md:py-16 px-4">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-8 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4">
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <div class="flex items-center space-x-2">
          <div class="relative h-10 w-10 bg-white rounded-full p-1">
            <Logo />
          </div>
          <span class="font-bold text-lg">Innov Africtivistes</span>
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm text-white/80">
          Une initiative stratégique visant à enrichir l'écosystème numérique d'Africtivistes en mettant en lumière
          des projets innovants qui promeuvent la démocratie, la gouvernance et l'engagement civique en Afrique.
        </p>
        <div class="flex space-x-4">
          <a
            href="https://facebook.com/africtivistes"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            aria-label="Facebook"
            class="bg-white/10 p-2 rounded-full hover:bg-white/20 transition-colors"
          >
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="h-5 w-5">
              <path d="M18 2h-3a5 5 0 0 0-5 5v3H7v4h3v8h4v-8h3l1-4h-4V7a1 1 0 0 1 1-1h3z"></path>
            </svg>
          </a>
          <a
            href="https://twitter.com/africtivistes"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            aria-label="Twitter"
            class="bg-white/10 p-2 rounded-full hover:bg-white/20 transition-colors"
          >
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="h-5 w-5">
              <path d="M22 4s-.7 2.1-2 3.4c1.6 10-9.4 17.3-18 11.6 2.2.1 4.4-.6 6-2C3 15.5.5 9.6 3 5c2.2 2.6 5.6 4.1 9 4-.9-4.2 4-6.6 7-3.8 1.1 0 3-1.2 3-1.2z"></path>
            </svg>
          </a>
          <a
            href="https://instagram.com/afric_tivistes"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            aria-label="Instagram"
            class="bg-white/10 p-2 rounded-full hover:bg-white/20 transition-colors"
          >
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="h-5 w-5">
              <rect x="2" y="2" width="20" height="20" rx="5" ry="5"></rect>
              <path d="M16 11.37A4 4 0 1 1 12.63 8 4 4 0 0 1 16 11.37z"></path>
              <line x1="17.5" y1="6.5" x2="17.51" y2="6.5"></line>
            </svg>
          </a>
          <a
            href="https://linkedin.com/company/africtivistes"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            aria-label="LinkedIn"
            class="bg-white/10 p-2 rounded-full hover:bg-white/20 transition-colors"
          >
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="h-5 w-5">
              <path d="M16 8a6 6 0 0 1 6 6v7h-4v-7a2 2 0 0 0-2-2 2 2 0 0 0-2 2v7h-4v-7a6 6 0 0 1 6-6z"></path>
              <rect x="2" y="9" width="4" height="12"></rect>
              <circle cx="4" cy="4" r="2"></circle>
            </svg>
          </a>
          <a
            href="https://youtube.com/africtivistes"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            aria-label="YouTube"
            class="bg-white/10 p-2 rounded-full hover:bg-white/20 transition-colors"
          >
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="h-5 w-5">
              <path d="M22.54 6.42a2.78 2.78 0 0 0-1.94-2C18.88 4 12 4 12 4s-6.88 0-8.6.46a2.78 2.78 0 0 0-1.94 2A29 29 0 0 0 1 11.75a29 29 0 0 0 .46 5.33A2.78 2.78 0 0 0 3.4 19c1.72.46 8.6.46 8.6.46s6.88 0 8.6-.46a2.78 2.78 0 0 0 1.94-2 29 29 0 0 0 .46-5.25 29 29 0 0 0-.46-5.33z"></path>
              <polygon points="9.75 15.02 15.5 11.75 9.75 8.48 9.75 15.02"></polygon>
            </svg>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h3 class="mb-4 text-lg font-medium">Liens rapides</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm">
          <li>
            <a href="/projets" class="hover:underline">
              Projets innovants
            </a>
          </li>
          <li>
            <a href="/partenaires" class="hover:underline">
              Nos partenaires
            </a>
          </li>
          <li>
            <a href="/ressources" class="hover:underline">
              Ressources
            </a>
          </li>
          <li>
            <a href="/actualites" class="hover:underline">
              Actualités
            </a>
          </li>
          <li>
            <a href="/evenements" class="hover:underline">
              Événements
            </a>
          </li>
          <li>
            <a href="/forum" class="hover:underline">
              Forum communautaire
            </a>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h3 class="mb-4 text-lg font-medium">Plateformes Africtivistes</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm">
          <li>
            <a
              href="https://africtivistes.com"
              target="_blank"
              rel="noopener noreferrer"
              class="hover:underline"
            >
              africtivistes.com
            </a>
          </li>
          <li>
            <a
              href="https://academy.africtivistes.org"
              target="_blank"
              rel="noopener noreferrer"
              class="hover:underline"
            >
              academy.africtivistes.org
            </a>
          </li>
          <li>
            <a
              href="https://mooc.africtivistes.org"
              target="_blank"
              rel="noopener noreferrer"
              class="hover:underline"
            >
              mooc.africtivistes.org
            </a>
          </li>
          <li>
            <a
              href="https://healthlab.africtivistes.org"
              target="_blank"
              rel="noopener noreferrer"
              class="hover:underline"
            >
              healthlab.africtivistes.org
            </a>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h3 class="mb-4 text-lg font-medium">Contact</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm">
          <li>
            <a href="mailto:info@africtivistes.org" class="hover:underline">
              info@africtivistes.org
            </a>
          </li>
          <li>
            <a href="tel:+221338375124" class="hover:underline">
              +221 33 837 51 24
            </a>
          </li>
          <li class="pt-4">
            <a href="/contact" class="hover:underline">
              Formulaire de contact
            </a>
          </li>
          <li>
            <a href="/newsletter" class="hover:underline">
              S'abonner à la newsletter
            </a>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-12 border-t border-white/20 pt-8 text-center text-sm text-white/70">
      <p>© {new Date().getFullYear()} Africtivistes. Tous droits réservés.</p>
      <div class="mt-2 flex justify-center space-x-6">
        <a href="/mentions-legales" class="hover:underline">
          Mentions légales
        </a>
        <a href="/politique-confidentialite" class="hover:underline">
          Politique de confidentialité
        </a>
        <a href="/conditions-utilisation" class="hover:underline">
          Conditions d'utilisation
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
